# Database Schema Diagram

**Purpose**: Complete database schema visualization showing all 27+ tables across 4 phases, plus ChromaDB collections and Redis cache patterns.

**Schema Evolution**:

### Phase 1-4: Core Tables
| Table | Purpose | Key Relationships |
|-------|---------|-------------------|
| `companies` | Company master data | Primary key for all financial data |
| `reports` | Generated research reports | FK → companies |
| `agent_runs` | Agent execution audit trail | FK → reports, companies |

### Phase 5: Knowledge Intelligence (13 tables)
| Table | Purpose | Key Indexes |
|-------|---------|-------------|
| `kg_nodes` | Knowledge graph entities | node_type, name, embedding (pgvector) |
| `kg_edges` | Knowledge graph relationships | source_id, target_id, relationship_type |
| `portfolios` | Portfolio definitions | owner_id |
| `positions` | Portfolio holdings | portfolio_id, symbol |
| `transactions` | Trade history | portfolio_id, symbol |
| `patterns` | Detected patterns | symbol, pattern_type, detected_at |
| `alerts` | Triggered alerts | watchlist_id, symbol, triggered_at |
| `alert_rules` | Alert configurations | watchlist_id |
| `analytics_runs` | Analytics executions | analysis_type, status |
| `factor_exposures` | Factor model results | run_id |
| `monte_carlo_paths` | Simulation paths | run_id |
| `historical_data` | Time-series storage | company_id, data_type, timestamp |
| `agent_memory` | Cross-agent memory | scope, scope_key, memory_type |

### Phase 7: Autonomous Research (1 table)
| Table | Purpose | Key Indexes |
|-------|---------|-------------|
| `research_sessions` | Autonomous research workflows | company, status, started_at |

### Phase 8: AI Copilot (11 tables)
| Table | Purpose | Key Indexes |
|-------|---------|-------------|
| `copilot_sessions` | User copilot sessions | user_id, company, status |
| `conversations` | Chat conversations | session_id, user_id |
| `conversation_messages` | Message history | conversation_id, timestamp |
| `decision_history` | Decision audit trail | session_id, conversation_id |
| `tool_executions` | Tool usage tracking | session_id, tool_name |
| `workflow_executions` | Workflow tracking | session_id, company, status |
| `long_term_memory` | Enhanced memory | scope, scope_key, importance |
| `conversation_memory` | Chat context | user_id, session_id |
| `user_preferences` | Learned preferences | user_id (PK) |
| `decision_history` | Outcome tracking | user_id, session_id |
| `tool_usage_analytics` | Tool analytics | user_id, tool_name, timestamp |

---

**ChromaDB Collections** (Vector Store):
| Collection | Content | Dimensions | Embedding Model |
|------------|---------|------------|-----------------|
| `financial_docs` | SEC filings, earnings, reports | 1024 | BGE-M3 |
| `news_articles` | News articles | 1024 | BGE-M3 |
| `earnings_transcripts` | Earnings calls | 1024 | BGE-M3 |
| `analyst_reports` | Analyst reports | 1024 | BGE-M3 |
| `market_data` | Market data embeddings | 1024 | BGE-M3 |

---

**Redis Cache Patterns**:
| Pattern | TTL | Purpose |
|---------|-----|---------|
| `session:{id}` | 24h | User session data |
| `ratelimit:{key}` | 1m-1h | Distributed rate limiting |
| `tool:{tool}:{hash}` | 5m-1h | Tool result caching |
| `llm:{model}:{hash}` | 1h | LLM response caching |
| `market:{ticker}:quote` | 5m | Real-time market data |

---

**Critical Indexes**:
```sql
-- Company lookups
CREATE INDEX idx_companies_ticker ON companies(ticker);
CREATE INDEX idx_companies_cik ON companies(cik);

-- Agent runs
CREATE INDEX idx_agent_runs_report ON agent_runs(report_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_agent_runs_agent ON agent_runs(agent_name);
CREATE INDEX idx_agent_runs_timestamp ON agent_runs(timestamp DESC);

-- Knowledge Graph
CREATE INDEX idx_kg_nodes_type ON kg_nodes(node_type);
CREATE INDEX idx_kg_edges_source ON kg_edges(source_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_kg_edges_target ON kg_edges(target_id);

-- Phase 8
CREATE INDEX idx_copilot_user ON copilot_sessions(user_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_msg_conversation ON conversation_messages(conversation_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_decision_session ON decision_history(session_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_ltm_scope_key ON long_term_memory(scope, scope_key);
CREATE INDEX idx_ltm_importance ON long_term_memory(importance);
